{"tid":2176214,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"隔牆有耳：網民Game廣傳7.21真相（李八方）","createTime":"2020-08-27T03:21:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-27T03:48:37.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"675c76a450fb32447fe3b2a77790d3adc7a63732","tid":2176214,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T03:21:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200827/WN6GNEO7ENC6BIN3BMSY37V75M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200827%2FWN6GNEO7ENC6BIN3BMSY37V75M%2F&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97Zvpk3GrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=f890981a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200827%2FWN6GNEO7ENC6BIN3BMSY37V75M%2F&h=f35d5d59\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200827/WN6GNEO7ENC6BIN3BMSY37V75M/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：網民Game廣傳7.21真相（李八方）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/L1i4YluFxdezdrlZrdkb4xq6ogg=/2634x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VIRLG2R5WFBGTIDY6SEIU3HKZQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FL1i4YluFxdezdrlZrdkb4xq6ogg%3D%2F2634x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVIRLG2R5WFBGTIDY6SEIU3HKZQ.jpg&h=db2b4b15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■參考港鐵站而成的背景畫面，畫有一大堆手持武器嘅白衣人。<br />\n<br />\n警方噚日企圖改寫7.21歷史，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/1H9keULr-z62Y2HAl-PjoKFYwSs=/2201x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MU2MVHJ3KVHIVDVURIYSPRG2JE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F1H9keULr-z62Y2HAl-PjoKFYwSs%3D%2F2201x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMU2MVHJ3KVHIVDVURIYSPRG2JE.jpg&h=74b17357&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■遊戲還原7.21市民以雨傘自保嘅畫面。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/tThhNKjpn7KL6VmF1B43YYqkbWQ=/2160x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PFPXIQEETRA3JN3ESQPO52QOE4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FtThhNKjpn7KL6VmF1B43YYqkbWQ%3D%2F2160x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPFPXIQEETRA3JN3ESQPO52QOE4.jpg&h=f3102ea6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■主人翁乘坐列車到目的地，為遊戲展開序幕。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n獲外國玩家介紹<br />\n<br />\n早排有網民係reddit發帖，題目叫「Made a game that is referenced to the 721 attack in Hong Kong」，介紹一隻佢自己以7.21做背景整嘅電腦遊戲，暫時只係有Demo，佢之後再喺連登發帖，話呢個係一隻2D風格RPG 遊戲，而個Demo嘅任務係主線任務之一，主要參考7.21無差別襲擊事件，當然細節有修改以符合遊戲世界，所以故事內容同角色都係純屬虛構，仲戴晒頭盔話「如有雷同，實屬巧合」！<br />\n<br />\n由於網民話佢仲讀緊書，空閒時間先可以寫game，而隻game嘅圖畫同音樂都係佢自己一手包辦，仲叫人如果想隻game可以畀更多人見到，可以下載試玩同畀好評，有外國YouTuber亦有介紹隻game。popo想改寫歷史，但時代唔同，唔再係你講乜都有信人，亦有人用不同方法，將7.21真相廣傳同保存，好似今次網民用game去記錄即為一例，有興趣可以去個game 嘅網址：<a href=\"https://mighcty.itch.io/legacy-of-datura\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmighcty.itch.io%2Flegacy-of-datura&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97Zvpk3GrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=9655aa8e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mighcty.itch.io/legacy-of-datura</a> 睇吓同下載試玩版。<br />\n<br />\n李八方"},{"pid":"7d305a94529be2db285288f8bb3a79f1e65edec0","tid":2176214,"uid":37894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T03:24:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"46a7ad149a53d536b00ff7e25e58bf0c0cc5c0e7","tid":2176214,"uid":117509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T03:25:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36c646b29dd66ff770d2f48a908728527ed276ca","tid":2176214,"uid":3290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T03:36:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj